node.text: wow. just wow. Can’t believe an unfinished car could look so good 😂Beyond excited with how the @streethunterdesigns C8 kit turned out. Some pieces are still missing off this car that already went into paint and hasn’t been lowered yet but this is the last photo you’ll see before it’s officially complete. Todays YouTube video provides a full walk around of the car and detailed look. Our team has been working SO hard on this one and I have to say we’ve truly perfected every aspect of this kit.
